.Dd $Mdocdate: May 3 2008 $
.Dt MPCPCIBR 4 macppc
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm mpcpcibr
.Nd PCI host bridge
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "mpcpcibr* at mainbus0"
.Cd "pci* at mpcpcibr?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the PCI host bridge present on PowerPC systems.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 2.2 .
